Allure Cosmetics Inc said itreached an agreement with &lt;Motown Industries> of Los Angeles tobe the exclusive licensee of the Motown name for skin care,cosmetics and hair-care products.    Allure said the medium-priced products are scheduled to beintroduced at a trade show in Philadelphia in early April. Thecompany said the products will be sold in professional salons,major drug chains and department stores.    Allure also said it entered into a merchandising agreementwith the U.S. Olympic Committee to use the Olympic designationon  suntan, sun treatment, lip care and otherfacial skin-care products.    Alllure said it also introduced a new face lift masque,intended to reduce wrinkles and other signs of aging. Reuter&#3;